            <article id="post-60547" class="post-60547 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-singularity tag-bitcoin tag-cryptocurrency tag-digital-world">       	
                <header class="entry-header">
                    <div class="entry-meta top">
                                                	<p class="meta top"><img alt='Jason Dorrier' src='http://cdn.singularityhub.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Jason-Dorrier_avatar-40x40.jpg' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' />Written By: <a href="http://singularityhub.com/author/jdorrier/" title="Posts by Jason Dorrier" rel="author">Jason Dorrier</a><br />Posted: 04/9/13 9:41 AM</p>
						                    </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
                    <div class="shareme top">
